producing 3 million barrels of oil a day back in the

00:43.526 --> 00:48.511
40s. They're probably producing less than 
300,000 barrels a day. and there's essentially no

00:54.233 --> 00:55.816
place to drill. It's just an area that was drilled 
over. Romania is the same thing. Romania was a huge

00:59.882 --> 01:05.752
producer in the 2030s and 40s, and they're 
essentially depleted. So barring the

01:05.772 --> 01:14.167
development of cold fusion or nuclear fusion, the 
oil industry is going to be around producing

01:05.772 --> 01:14.167
energy. They're going to be around producing 
energy, predominantly gas. Gas production in

